No. 338,

Misc.

Gambale v. Massachusetts. Robert H. Quinn, Attorney General of Massachusetts, John Wall, Assistant Attorney General, and Lawrence P. Cohen, Deputy Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Sup. Jud. Ct. Mass. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that cer-tiorari should be granted.
